title: Soccer stars and Liberia's new president arrive at Elysee Palace
text:
Soccer stars and Liberia's new president arrive at Elysee Palace 5:03pm GMT - 00:45 
French President Emmanuel Macron received Liberia's Weah and soccer players Mbappe and Drogba at the Elysee Palace in Paris. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
